Daimler CFO ‘Optimistic’ Over Tognum Offer, Welt Reports

-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 
2011-04-09T10:41:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-09/daimler-cfo-optimistic-over-tognum-offer-welt-reports.html
Daimler AG (DAI)  is “optimistic” its
joint offer for German engine manufacturer Tognum AG will be
accepted by enough shareholders and doesn’t plan to increase its
offer,  Die Welt  reported today, citing an interview with
Daimler’s Chief Financial Officer Bodo Uebber.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
